JOHANNESBURG Prize money for the 2019 Africa Cup of Nations in Egypt: Champions: Sh407 million ($4 million, 3.57 million euros) Runners-up: Sh203 million ($2 million) Semi-finalists: Sh104 million ($1.5 million) Quarter-finalists: Sh81 million ($800,000) Groups/third: Sh58 million ($575,000) Groups/fourth: Sh48 million ($475,000) Total: $16.4 million  